Package: InquisitR
Type: Package
Title: InquisitR: Package for Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nathan Bresette
Maintainer: Nathan Bresette <nathanbresette04@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Description: 
    InquisitR is a package designed for data analysis and visualization in R. It provides functions for creating bar plots for categorical variables and histograms for numeric variables in a given data frame. The package aims to streamline the process of exploratory data analysis and visualization.
